73
00:06:52,219 --> 00:06:53,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

74
00:06:54,089 --> 00:06:55,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pasti lihat hal-hal lagi.</font>

75
00:06:55,989 --> 00:06:58,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, aku tak percaya kau juga begitu di sini.</font>

76
00:07:00,159 --> 00:07:01,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kulakukan, Bok Ja?</font>

