00:08:02,559 --> 00:08:03,759
<font color=#FFFF00>kerusakan properti.</font>

94
00:08:05,719 --> 00:08:07,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan!</font>

95
00:08:07,389 --> 00:08:08,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

96
00:08:11,559 --> 00:08:13,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Terakhir, karena kau berkelahi di sebuah kafe,</font>

97
00:08:13,919 --> 00:08:16,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasal 314 KUHP, gangguan bisnis juga berlaku.</font>

98
00:08:16,919 --> 00:08:18,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu terjadi begitu saja.</font>

99
00:08:19,619 --> 00:08:22,789
