103
00:08:30,419 --> 00:08:32,219
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi kau tidak bisa berdamai.</font>

104
00:08:32,219 --> 00:08:34,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku tidak bisa.</font>

105
00:08:35,819 --> 00:08:37,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memulai perselisihan, bukan?</font>

106
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, begitulah.</font>

107
00:08:39,659 --> 00:08:42,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa itu terjadi begitu?
