761
00:59:29,418 --> 00:59:30,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita semua...</font>

762
00:59:31,378 --> 00:59:32,848
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernah kehilangan seseorang.</font>

763
00:59:39,678 --> 00:59:41,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Beberapa kehilangan anggota keluarga.</font>

764
00:59:41,818 --> 00:59:43,148
