00:59:49,018 --> 00:59:50,148
<font color=#FFFF00>tak ada orang...</font>

768
00:59:50,818 --> 00:59:52,748
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang tidak kehilangan sesorang...</font>

769
00:59:53,678 --> 00:59:55,118
<font color=#FFFF00>...dalam perjalanan hidup mereka.</font>

770
