791
01:02:30,278 --> 01:02:31,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Lama tak bertemu, temanku.</font>

792
01:02:32,578 --> 01:02:34,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Bong Hee, kau tak apa?</font>

793
01:02:34,918 --> 01:02:37,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin kita berpisah dan melewatinya?
