794
01:02:37,918 --> 01:02:39,078
<font color=#FFFF00>...melewatinya bersama-sama?</font>

795
01:02:39,118 --> 01:02:41,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin kau ada di sisiku
saat kita melewati semua ini.</font>

796
01:02:47,008 --> 01:02:48,078
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak ada orang di sini, kan?</font>

797
01:02:50,248 --> 01:02:51,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan taruh di sini.</font>

798
01:02:58,378 --> 01:03:00,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Kantor kita yang berantakan!</font>

799
01:03:00,378 --> 01:03:02,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong bantu cari uang!</font>

